  "filename": "remoting.md",
  "__html": "<h1 id=\"remoting%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B\">remoting存储类型 <a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#remoting%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B\">#</a></h1>\n<p>连接模式为<a href=\"/zh-cn/docs/tutorial/connectionmode/server.html\">server模式</a>时就是用的这种存储类型。<br>\n使用这种存储类型，客户端不在直接存储和任务的相关操作，简化了tcc配置同时减轻系统负担。</p>\n<h2 id=\"%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\">如何使用 <a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\">#</a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83\">选择注册中心 <a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83\">#</a></h3>\n<p>查看<a href=\"/zh-cn/docs/tutorial/registry/index.html\">注册中心说明</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"server%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2\">server部署 <a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#server%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2\">#</a></h3>\n<p>查看<a href=\"/zh-cn/docs/ops/server/index.html\">server部署说明</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\">添加配置 <a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\">#</a></h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"hljs-attr\">spring:</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">tcc:</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">storage:</span>\n      <span class=\"hljs-attr\">storage-type:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">remoting</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">registry:</span>\n      <span class=\"hljs-attr\">registry-type:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">direct</span>\n      <span class=\"hljs-attr\">cluster-name:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">default</span>\n      <span class=\"hljs-attr\">direct:</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">server-addresses:</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">127.0</span><span class=\"hljs-number\">.0</span><span class=\"hljs-number\">.1</span><span class=\"hljs-string\">:2332</span>\n      <span class=\"hljs-attr\">zookeeper:</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">connect-string:</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">127.0</span><span class=\"hljs-number\">.0</span><span class=\"hljs-number\">.1</span><span class=\"hljs-string\">:2181</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">max-retries:</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>\n      <span class=\"hljs-attr\">nacos:</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">server-addr:</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">127.0</span><span class=\"hljs-number\">.0</span><span class=\"hljs-number\">.1</span><span class=\"hljs-string\">:8848</span>\n</code></pre>\n",
  "link": "/zh-cn/docs/tutorial/storagetype/remoting.html",
  "meta": {}
}